The game must keep track of score as the user plays. 
	Score will reset once player crashes.
	High score will be kept.
The controls must allow the player to move forward, backward, left, and right. 

The game must get progressively harder the longer the player plays. 
	Speed of user will get faster as time moves on.
	User will reach max speed after a fixed amount of
	time.

The player will only have one life.

Obstacles must be in varying positions like center, right, left of road. 
	There must always be a path for user to go through. 
This game must be in third person.
	The perspective will be from the back of the car.
User can input name when getting high score.
	Input validation must be done for this.
User must be bound to road, cannot drive off of road.  
